{"tid":2157564,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★象山邨居民：我想回內地逛街、吃東西、遊玩，現在也不行，經常在香港也很悶","createTime":"2020-08-15T06:16:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T07:47:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"de42fb74cc229ee9e9170ae7c03665e1391ba96c","tid":2157564,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:16:09.000Z","msg":"對於有建議推行「健康碼」，有健康碼才可到商場、食肆，居民反應兩極。  秀山樓居民說：「我想去哪是大家個人自由，健康碼並不完全代表那個人當刻是絕對安全，亦有誤測可能性。這樣的情況下限制一個人的基本人身自由，是有值得商榷的地方。」  另一名秀山樓居民說：「我想回內地逛街、吃東西、遊玩，現在也不行，經常在香港也很悶，我想出外，有健康碼證明我沒事便很好。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5f376c17335d193046692ca6/民政署擴大社區檢測計劃-荃灣象山邨收集咽拭子樣本\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5f376c17335d193046692ca6%2F%E6%B0%91%E6%94%BF%E7%BD%B2%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E8%B1%A1%E5%B1%B1%E9%82%A8%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%E5%92%BD%E6%8B%AD%E5%AD%90%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8d%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=a939c717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5f376c17335d193046692ca6/民政署擴大社區檢測計劃-荃灣象山邨收集咽拭子樣本</a>"},{"pid":"22e79a4bf03c777f1619bbfdbe32745f441e6f45","tid":2157564,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:16:31.000Z","msg":"never come back<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oicc2z8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foicc2z8.jpg&h=cfc842f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73eb5b7fa04db04e1fffd931d6a349dc556e5a9f","tid":2157564,"uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nKDjG2P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnKDjG2P.gif&h=89f78449&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2290c62702ee2565a86380139d9f64b269477e30","tid":2157564,"uid":8435,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06: